Sentencas: In this paper, a uniform and defective LaSrCoO4 was prepared by using amino acid derived surfactant (N-(2-hydroxylalkyl)-L-Phenylalanine).
Titulo: Facile synthesis of uniform LaSrCoO4 using amino acid-derived surfactant and its utilization as an excellent cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Owing to rich active groups of N-(2-hydroxylalkyl)-L-Phenylalanine, the resultant LaSrCoO4 showed enhanced specific surface area and good electro-catalytic property.
Titulo: Facile synthesis of uniform LaSrCoO4 using amino acid-derived surfactant and its utilization as an excellent cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The porous K2NiF4-type LaSrCoO4 was verified as a good cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Facile synthesis of uniform LaSrCoO4 using amino acid-derived surfactant and its utilization as an excellent cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The LaSrCoO4 electrode demonstrated good electrochemical performance, including good electrical conductivity (138.7 S cm(-1), in air at 800 degrees C), low polarization resistance R-p (0.108 Omega cm(2), symmetric cells in air at 800 degrees C) and high power densities (688 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C).
Titulo: Facile synthesis of uniform LaSrCoO4 using amino acid-derived surfactant and its utilization as an excellent cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The as-prepared LaSrCoO4 shows a promising application as the cathode materials in the intermediate temperature SOFCs.
Titulo: Facile synthesis of uniform LaSrCoO4 using amino acid-derived surfactant and its utilization as an excellent cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell
